settings.description: To carry a flurry, press the run button when above it on a semisolid. Can be used in Freezeflame Manor.
A long and vegetable filled adventure. A mini Mario game I guess?
Esquiva la balas y no te resvales en el hielo, buena suerte.

Just keep running, and don't stop! Let the triangular blocks guide you!
Difficulty: 2/5

The wigglers invade the green mountains,and the galoombas,enjoy.     sorry for the bugs :C
